WEBVTT

01:34.080 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:38.320 --> 01:43.720
YIHE UNIVERSITY

01:48.520 --> 01:49.600
Mom.

01:49.680 --> 01:51.120
Where are you?

01:51.200 --> 01:53.280
Three of us, six eyes,
but we still can't find you!

01:54.600 --> 01:55.600
The graduation ceremony is over.

01:55.680 --> 01:57.720
Our family should have a meal together.

01:58.280 --> 01:59.640
I'm meeting friends.

02:00.320 --> 02:01.960
I'm having dinner with Qian Fei
and the others tonight.

02:02.040 --> 02:03.120
That's it. I'll hang up.

02:04.520 --> 02:05.560
What did he say?

02:06.720 --> 02:08.080
He's not eating with us.

02:08.600 --> 02:10.080
We've been waiting for him for so long.

02:10.160 --> 02:11.560
- So annoying!
- Don't say that.

02:11.640 --> 02:12.680
- Let's check over there.
- This kid.

02:12.760 --> 02:14.320
- He's always annoying.
- Let's keep looking.

02:19.000 --> 02:21.040
- Time for the graduation photo!
- Hurry up!

02:26.080 --> 02:27.600
Gather up!

02:27.680 --> 02:29.320
Everyone gather up!

02:29.400 --> 02:30.760
Come on. Gather up!

02:32.880 --> 02:33.800
Wen Yifan.

02:34.320 --> 02:36.040
- Come on!
- Wen Yifan!

02:38.360 --> 02:39.440
Wen Yifan!

02:40.080 --> 02:41.920
You guys go ahead. Yifan!

02:42.000 --> 02:43.600
- Yifan!
- Yifan!

02:44.200 --> 02:46.720
Guys at the back, fold your umbrellas.

02:49.840 --> 02:53.120
- Yifan, come quickly.
- Okay, everyone find a spot.

02:53.840 --> 02:55.200
Everyone, smile.

02:56.400 --> 02:58.480
Three, two, one.

02:58.560 --> 03:00.720
Cheese!

03:00.800 --> 03:02.480
Come on. One more picture.
Everyone, jump up

03:02.560 --> 03:03.400
and shout "Happy Graduation"!

03:03.480 --> 03:04.560
Okay.

03:04.640 --> 03:06.320
Happy Graduation!

03:09.160 --> 03:10.240
One more picture.

03:11.680 --> 03:13.160
Alright, check it out.

03:13.240 --> 03:14.200
You know what?

03:14.280 --> 03:17.280
Just now, I saw a super handsome guy!

03:17.360 --> 03:18.960
- Really?
- For real?

03:19.040 --> 03:20.040
I don't know which department he's from.

03:20.120 --> 03:22.560
Yifan, when Xin just called you,
why didn't you react?

03:22.640 --> 03:24.480
Were you looking
at that handsome guy, too?

03:24.560 --> 03:26.080
I just heard someone calling my name.

03:26.160 --> 03:28.120
That was me calling you!

03:28.200 --> 03:30.040
The picture didn't turn out well.
Let's take another one.

03:30.120 --> 03:31.200
One more.

03:33.480 --> 03:34.760
- Take a look.
- You guys go ahead.

03:34.840 --> 03:35.760
Okay.

03:54.240 --> 03:55.680
How could it be him?

04:11.600 --> 04:12.440
3,446 DAYS

04:15.200 --> 04:16.800
- Alright, this is for you.
- It's time to eat.

04:16.880 --> 04:18.240
You can only have one of these.

04:19.839 --> 04:22.440
Haoan, this is a home-cooked dish I made.

04:23.360 --> 04:26.080
This dish is my favorite.

04:28.080 --> 04:29.040
Here.

04:29.120 --> 04:30.440
- Su, taste it.
- It's dirty.

04:30.520 --> 04:31.640
It's dirty.

04:31.720 --> 04:33.080
You should use the serving chopsticks!

04:33.640 --> 04:35.440
I'm just being kind.

04:35.520 --> 04:37.640
Grandpa, he's a guest.

04:37.720 --> 04:39.280
- Exactly.
- Isn't he

04:39.360 --> 04:41.760
- Qiao's boyfriend?
- What boyfriend?

04:41.840 --> 04:44.840
If not married,
he's still a guest, Grandpa.

04:44.920 --> 04:46.200
- Let's eat. If we keep talking,
- Okay.

04:46.280 --> 04:48.360
Su will feel embarrassed.

04:48.440 --> 04:49.880
- Come on.
- Have some.

04:49.960 --> 04:51.320
- Come on.
- Thank you.

04:51.400 --> 04:53.560
How about having a drink?

04:54.200 --> 04:56.120
Sure. I'll drink with you.

04:56.200 --> 04:57.480
Great.

04:58.880 --> 05:00.440
Make yourself at home.

05:00.960 --> 05:03.120
When I visit my grandparents,
it's always like this.

05:03.640 --> 05:04.680
Just imagine

05:04.760 --> 05:07.120
how comfortable you feel
when you eat alone.

05:07.200 --> 05:08.200
Like the last time I was at your place,

05:08.280 --> 05:09.400
the carefree way of you eating breakfast.

05:15.960 --> 05:17.960
Mr. Su, what are you laughing at?

05:20.920 --> 05:24.040
Nothing. I just had a beautiful dream.

05:24.120 --> 05:25.360
Tell me about it!

05:25.440 --> 05:27.120
I'm not telling you.

05:28.280 --> 05:29.480
Don't fantasize about that.

05:43.560 --> 05:44.440
Have one.

05:45.440 --> 05:46.920
I didn't.

05:47.000 --> 05:47.840
Here.

05:48.960 --> 05:49.960
I toast to you.

05:50.880 --> 05:51.960
Have one.

05:54.440 --> 05:55.720
Drink less.

05:55.800 --> 05:58.440
We were supposed to take you
to a nice restaurant today.

05:59.000 --> 05:59.840
No need.

05:59.920 --> 06:02.080
Dad, you don't have to be so nice to him.

06:02.160 --> 06:04.440
She said that. I can only listen to her.

06:04.520 --> 06:05.840
Actually, I really like eating here.

06:05.920 --> 06:07.120
- Really?
- I just love

06:07.200 --> 06:08.840
having the family eat together.

06:08.920 --> 06:11.720
When you all greeted me
from the window last time,

06:11.800 --> 06:12.920
I thought to myself,

06:13.000 --> 06:14.000
if I could have a meal with you,

06:14.080 --> 06:15.400
that would be wonderful.

06:15.480 --> 06:18.480
- Our big family is always lively.
- Right.

06:18.560 --> 06:20.840
- Just treat this place like your home.
- Okay.

06:20.920 --> 06:21.960
- Eat more.
- Don't be shy.

06:22.040 --> 06:23.920
Then I won't be shy anymore!

06:24.000 --> 06:24.920
- Okay, eat up.
- Don't be shy.

06:25.000 --> 06:26.240
Eat up.

06:31.200 --> 06:32.280
Are you full?

06:33.520 --> 06:34.760
Very full.

06:34.840 --> 06:35.960
That's good.

06:37.240 --> 06:39.280
Eating with your family

06:39.360 --> 06:41.000
feels so happy and so joyful.

06:41.080 --> 06:43.120
- Really?
- Thank you.

06:44.200 --> 06:45.040
Okay.

06:49.600 --> 06:50.600
I always

06:51.360 --> 06:52.440
imagine…

06:53.880 --> 06:55.280
if my dad were still alive,

06:56.160 --> 06:58.000
I'd want to live a life like this,

06:58.080 --> 06:59.000
eating meals together

06:59.080 --> 07:00.440
and chatting together.

07:04.000 --> 07:05.120
You know what?

07:05.960 --> 07:06.800
Back then,

07:07.560 --> 07:09.240
I stood right here.

07:09.960 --> 07:11.600
I thought about jumping.

07:13.680 --> 07:14.800
If I had jumped,

07:14.880 --> 07:17.920
all this happiness now wouldn't exist.

07:20.440 --> 07:21.440
Luckily.

07:22.760 --> 07:25.120
Yeah. Luckily.

07:29.080 --> 07:30.600
As long as we're alive,

07:30.680 --> 07:33.280
we'll always have hope and dreams.

07:34.440 --> 07:35.480
So,

07:36.520 --> 07:37.880
I decided to talk to her mom…

07:37.960 --> 07:39.000
What are you guys doing?

07:39.880 --> 07:41.680
The fruit's ready. Come back and eat!

07:41.760 --> 07:43.200
- Come back!
- Hurry up!

07:43.280 --> 07:44.360
Okay!

07:56.600 --> 07:57.720
You're here.

07:57.800 --> 07:59.720
You're looking for our boss, right?
He's upstairs.

08:00.640 --> 08:02.400
Okay, then I'll go up directly.

08:02.480 --> 08:04.280
- Want to have a drink?
- No, thanks.

08:23.000 --> 08:24.960
Shuangjiang, it's really you.

08:25.480 --> 08:27.000
I knew I wasn't wrong.

08:30.680 --> 08:31.600
Is something wrong?

08:33.159 --> 08:35.919
What do you mean?
How can you talk to me this way, kid?

08:37.440 --> 08:39.520
The last time you saw me,
you even pretended not to know me.

08:40.039 --> 08:41.080
Yifan,

08:41.600 --> 08:42.760
it's been so long
since you've seen your uncle,

08:42.840 --> 08:43.960
and you didn't even say hello?

08:44.960 --> 08:45.800
Shuangjiang.

08:48.880 --> 08:49.840
Are you okay?

08:52.520 --> 08:53.400
Who are you?

08:54.080 --> 08:55.320
Who am I?

08:55.400 --> 08:57.840
- I'm her uncle. Who are you?
- He's not.

08:59.600 --> 09:00.440
What?

09:02.200 --> 09:04.600
I'm not your uncle?
Shuangjiang, can you really say that?

09:04.680 --> 09:06.120
I used to support you.

09:06.200 --> 09:08.040
Don't you remember? Did you forget?

09:08.120 --> 09:09.040
Do you know him?

09:11.280 --> 09:12.200
No.

09:13.040 --> 09:14.240
Move aside!

09:16.600 --> 09:17.480
Shuangjiang, where are you going?

09:18.440 --> 09:19.720
Let go of her!

09:20.320 --> 09:21.960
Don't you understand what I'm saying?

09:26.200 --> 09:27.200
What do you mean?

09:27.800 --> 09:29.080
The boss is bullying me?

09:29.160 --> 09:30.960
What? You want to hit me?

09:31.760 --> 09:32.800
Who hit you?

09:34.000 --> 09:36.960
Oh, here comes another one.
Come on. Hit me.

09:37.040 --> 09:38.640
How come I didn't see anyone hit you?

09:39.480 --> 09:42.000
You mean, you want to fight
with someone, huh?

09:43.400 --> 09:45.920
Fine. I'm outnumbered and you're tough.

09:46.680 --> 09:47.520
Shuangjiang.

09:48.880 --> 09:49.760
See you next time.

10:03.200 --> 10:04.040
Does it hurt?

10:07.320 --> 10:08.160
Who's that?

10:11.360 --> 10:12.880
My aunt's brother.

10:13.400 --> 10:14.800
He doesn't really count as an uncle.

10:16.480 --> 10:17.600
Does he always act like that?

10:20.000 --> 10:21.040
I mean his attitude towards you.

10:23.600 --> 10:24.960
I'm not really close to him.

10:25.480 --> 10:27.040
He's not a good person either.

10:27.920 --> 10:29.240
If he comes again next time,

10:29.320 --> 10:31.840
just treat him like a stranger
and ignore him.

10:40.080 --> 10:41.080
Have a seat.

10:42.920 --> 10:44.320
Wait for me. I'll be right back.

11:02.000 --> 11:03.240
If you face any problem,

11:04.360 --> 11:05.200
you can tell me.

11:07.880 --> 11:08.720
Anything.

11:13.360 --> 11:15.320
Don't worry. It's nothing serious.

11:16.200 --> 11:17.240
Really.

11:17.960 --> 11:19.160
I can solve it myself.

11:20.040 --> 11:21.040
Go ahead and get busy.

11:32.200 --> 11:33.480
Let go of her!

11:33.560 --> 11:35.000
Don't you understand what I'm saying?

12:40.000 --> 12:41.920
Why do you always stare at the clock?

12:59.520 --> 13:02.600
All alone in the living room,
aren't you afraid?

13:06.160 --> 13:07.680
I won't lock the door anymore, okay?

13:10.320 --> 13:11.160
You can come find me.

13:27.520 --> 13:28.520
How are you doing?

13:30.720 --> 13:32.360
Why are you always crying?

15:00.120 --> 15:01.440
Do you want me to sleep with you?

15:06.000 --> 15:06.840
What if…

15:10.480 --> 15:12.040
you're secretly crying
again after I leave?

15:19.520 --> 15:20.520
Then…

15:21.960 --> 15:23.360
How about we go to my room?

16:31.160 --> 16:32.200
Sorry.

17:45.800 --> 17:48.560
This is… my room.

17:59.120 --> 18:00.640
This is my room.

18:02.240 --> 18:03.400
I know.

18:04.160 --> 18:05.640
Then, why are you here?

18:10.000 --> 18:11.440
Why am I here?

18:12.000 --> 18:12.880
Who else would be here, if not me?

18:13.720 --> 18:16.080
It really hurts to hear that.

18:17.080 --> 18:19.200
I mean, how come you're here?

18:20.960 --> 18:22.320
How come I'm here?

18:22.880 --> 18:24.120
What do you think? How would I be here?

18:25.240 --> 18:26.360
Think about it.

18:29.280 --> 18:30.160
You're sleepwalking, too?

18:32.120 --> 18:32.960
Sleepwalking can be contagious?

18:36.120 --> 18:37.720
Fine, believe what you want.

18:40.640 --> 18:42.000
Did you have a nightmare?

18:47.840 --> 18:50.920
Or did you watch
a horror movie last night,

18:51.000 --> 18:52.640
scared yourself, and couldn't sleep?

18:52.720 --> 18:54.000
That's why you came here?

18:54.080 --> 18:55.040
That's not it.

18:58.600 --> 19:01.160
So, you just wanted to sleep with me.

19:03.200 --> 19:04.160
Think about it again.

19:08.680 --> 19:10.240
You sleepwalked last night,

19:10.320 --> 19:11.960
barged into my room, lifted my blanket,

19:12.040 --> 19:13.920
and carried me over.

19:14.000 --> 19:16.080
How could I carry you?

19:23.240 --> 19:25.560
So, sleepwalking gives you
super strength, huh?

19:25.640 --> 19:26.960
I guess I'm pretty tough after all.

19:28.640 --> 19:29.800
What are you laughing at?

19:30.840 --> 19:31.680
I just want to laugh.

19:34.600 --> 19:35.800
Sang Yan.

19:36.440 --> 19:37.680
I'm Wen Yifan.

19:37.760 --> 19:39.720
Only you and Sang Yan
haven't shown up on the list.

19:39.800 --> 19:42.280
Sorry. I thought Sang Yan
was a girl's name.

19:42.360 --> 19:43.800
- I thought it was you.
- Report.

19:48.600 --> 19:50.120
Let's sleep a little longer.

19:53.480 --> 19:54.720
Apart from the name,

19:55.880 --> 19:57.000
my strength is more manly than yours.

19:59.000 --> 20:00.440
Alright, you're right.

20:01.480 --> 20:02.960
Sleep a bit more.

20:03.040 --> 20:03.880
I'll make you breakfast.

20:14.240 --> 20:15.320
Is it good?

20:17.200 --> 20:18.320
It melts in the mouth.

20:19.000 --> 20:20.000
It's smooth and tasty.

20:20.520 --> 20:22.840
Is "melts in the mouth"
a good description for noodles?

20:24.800 --> 20:26.120
It's just like that.

20:30.200 --> 20:32.120
- Did I make any progress?
- Of course.

20:41.720 --> 20:42.880
Sang Yan,

20:43.800 --> 20:47.200
if the guy from yesterday
comes to you at Overtime,

20:47.720 --> 20:50.480
no matter what he says or what he wants,

20:51.160 --> 20:52.080
just ignore him.

20:55.840 --> 20:57.320
What are you thinking?

20:57.400 --> 21:00.120
After being with you,
I've never spoken to strangers,

21:00.200 --> 21:01.560
neither to men nor women.

21:02.480 --> 21:04.720
And besides you,

21:05.240 --> 21:08.160
who can casually take something from me?

21:40.600 --> 21:43.080
Wait a minute! Elevator, hold on!

21:46.680 --> 21:47.680
Good morning, Yifan.

21:48.360 --> 21:50.000
Mr. Xingde, please
put my stuff here for now.

21:50.080 --> 21:50.920
This elevator's too crowded.

21:51.000 --> 21:51.840
- Let's wait for the next one.
- Alright.

21:51.920 --> 21:53.160
I'll leave it here. Remember to take it.

21:53.240 --> 21:54.400
Okay. Thanks, Mr. Xingde.

21:54.480 --> 21:56.040
No problem. Go ahead and get to work.

22:35.640 --> 22:36.560
Mu,

22:37.640 --> 22:38.960
the guy earlier,

22:39.480 --> 22:40.720
that Mr. Xingde,

22:40.800 --> 22:42.320
when did he become a security guard here?

22:43.200 --> 22:44.360
Just recently.

22:44.440 --> 22:46.720
The security near our TV station
isn't very good.

22:46.800 --> 22:48.080
So, he applied for the position.

22:48.160 --> 22:50.040
He's actually quite honest.
And he's very helpful.

22:50.120 --> 22:52.200
He often helps me move equipment.

22:52.840 --> 22:54.760
What's going on?
You've never met him before?

22:56.040 --> 22:57.600
No. It's my first time meeting him.

22:57.680 --> 23:00.440
Yifan, will you come
to my farewell party tonight?

23:01.800 --> 23:03.640
- See you tonight.
- I'll be a little late.

23:03.720 --> 23:04.920
I still have some drafts to handle.

23:05.000 --> 23:06.520
It's okay. I'll wait for you.

23:25.400 --> 23:27.600
QIU NIANGNIANG HOTPOT

23:27.680 --> 23:28.880
Toast to you, Chengyun!

23:28.960 --> 23:30.680
Are you toasting to him alone
or to all of us?

23:30.760 --> 23:31.760
Yeah.

23:31.840 --> 23:32.760
We toast to you all.

23:32.840 --> 23:34.480
- Come on!
- Let's drink together.

23:44.920 --> 23:45.840
Hello?

23:45.920 --> 23:48.800
Hello, Yifan. Today's my farewell party.

23:48.880 --> 23:50.000
If you don't come,

23:50.080 --> 23:52.520
you might never see me again.

23:52.600 --> 23:54.400
Okay, I'm on my way.

23:58.200 --> 23:59.440
When will you get off work?

23:59.520 --> 24:01.120
‪SANG YAN

24:01.200 --> 24:02.760
If you finish early, go home.

24:02.840 --> 24:03.720
Don't wait for me.

24:03.800 --> 24:05.520
I'm going out to eat with my colleagues.

24:28.680 --> 24:30.600
Miss Wen, you're off work.

24:33.800 --> 24:34.960
Stay safe.

24:51.920 --> 24:52.800
Shuangjiang.

25:04.000 --> 25:06.680
What's wrong? Did you see a ghost?

25:07.280 --> 25:08.480
What do you want to do?

25:11.120 --> 25:12.080
If you can return to Nanwu,

25:13.520 --> 25:14.400
why can't I?

25:15.080 --> 25:16.440
No matter what misunderstandings
we had before,

25:17.200 --> 25:19.600
I've explained everything to you.
It's just that you didn't listen.

25:19.680 --> 25:20.680
Misunderstanding?

25:20.760 --> 25:22.160
Yes. A misunderstanding.

25:24.040 --> 25:26.560
Do you know how I spent those days?

25:28.640 --> 25:30.320
I felt like I was dying.

25:31.240 --> 25:32.720
Each day felt like a year.

25:33.760 --> 25:35.800
Don't you think
what you're saying is absurd?

25:43.240 --> 25:45.640
Did I delay your college admission?

25:45.720 --> 25:47.440
Or did I affect your work?

25:48.240 --> 25:51.080
Or did I affect you dating
that rich boyfriend?

25:51.160 --> 25:52.280
I didn't.

25:52.960 --> 25:53.800
But because of you,

25:54.480 --> 25:57.360
my life changed since then.

25:57.440 --> 25:59.600
It became like this, worthless.

25:59.680 --> 26:00.920
Who am I supposed
to tell my grievances to?

26:05.360 --> 26:06.800
Shuangjiang, right now…

26:07.880 --> 26:09.640
I'm in trouble. You'll help me, right?

26:11.000 --> 26:11.840
Right?

26:20.960 --> 26:21.800
I'm telling you.

26:22.880 --> 26:24.280
If I can't make it through,

26:25.280 --> 26:28.240
no matter where you are, I'll find you.

26:28.320 --> 26:29.960
And I'll tell everyone

26:31.600 --> 26:34.320
that you once seduced me. Right?

26:34.400 --> 26:36.200
You even tried to kill me before.

26:37.240 --> 26:38.840
Even if no one believes me,

26:39.360 --> 26:42.160
you can't wash off
this dirt from yourself.

26:42.240 --> 26:44.760
Because the way I am now
is all because of you.

26:44.840 --> 26:47.160
You have to take responsibility
for me. Right?

26:48.200 --> 26:49.560
Yifan.

26:49.640 --> 26:51.720
Mr. Xingde? What are you doing here?

26:51.800 --> 26:53.960
It's nothing. I… I just got off work.

26:54.040 --> 26:56.440
I saw her alone here,
so I came over to talk to her.

26:57.240 --> 26:58.120
You're really responsible.

26:58.200 --> 26:59.920
It's okay. I'll head out first.

27:00.000 --> 27:00.840
Alright.

27:01.680 --> 27:03.040
Be careful on your way home.

27:10.920 --> 27:12.360
Are you alright, Yifan?

27:13.000 --> 27:13.880
I'm fine.

27:21.520 --> 27:23.640
Let's go then, Yifan.
Everyone's waiting for you.

27:38.840 --> 27:39.840
What a coincidence!

27:39.920 --> 27:41.600
Come on!

27:41.680 --> 27:42.720
Come on!

27:43.360 --> 27:45.520
Let's all toast to Mu Chengyun.
How about it?

27:45.600 --> 27:48.000
Let's wish him great success!

27:48.080 --> 27:49.240
And when he becomes famous,
don't forget us!

27:49.320 --> 27:50.720
- Okay!
- Come on!

27:50.800 --> 27:51.640
Come on!

27:51.720 --> 27:53.320
Once you make it, don't forget us!

27:53.400 --> 27:55.520
Empty it! Mu Chengyun, no cheating!

27:55.600 --> 27:57.200
Empty it…

28:10.560 --> 28:12.080
How come you're here?

28:12.160 --> 28:13.800
What a coincidence.

28:16.280 --> 28:18.560
No one eats with me. I'm so hungry, too.

28:19.840 --> 28:21.680
Did you just finish work?
Or did you come from Overtime?

28:21.760 --> 28:24.720
No, I didn't come from Overtime.
I just finished work.

28:26.600 --> 28:27.800
Who's leaving?

28:27.880 --> 28:29.680
Mu Chengyun. He officially resigned today.

28:31.760 --> 28:33.480
That's a bit of a shame.

28:34.200 --> 28:35.880
He seems pretty happy about it.

28:36.520 --> 28:38.080
He always wanted to be an actor.

28:40.440 --> 28:43.760
Now he's doing something he loves.
That's pretty good…

28:43.840 --> 28:44.840
ZHAO YUANDONG

28:46.840 --> 28:47.720
A while ago,

28:47.800 --> 28:50.120
Che Xingde went out
with a friend for a drive

28:50.200 --> 28:51.360
and had a car accident.

28:51.440 --> 28:52.640
That's really bad!

28:52.720 --> 28:54.080
He crashed into someone's shop.

28:54.160 --> 28:55.920
I was going to get them to move out.

28:56.000 --> 28:58.320
He promised me he would work hard.

28:58.400 --> 29:00.640
I heard he's found a decent job now.

29:01.680 --> 29:02.800
Don't worry.

29:11.560 --> 29:13.920
What's wrong? You're not happy?

29:14.680 --> 29:17.280
No. I just want to go home.

29:18.400 --> 29:19.640
If something's bothering you,
just tell me.

29:23.840 --> 29:25.920
Today, I visited kids with rare diseases.

29:27.160 --> 29:29.560
They're so young,
yet already face life and death.

29:30.560 --> 29:32.640
And they had no expression on their faces.

29:33.640 --> 29:35.240
It made me feel so sad.

29:39.760 --> 29:40.880
They'll get better.

29:47.200 --> 29:48.880
You're so focused on watching TV.

29:50.720 --> 29:51.840
Haven't you slept yet?

29:55.920 --> 29:58.360
Not yet. We'll sleep in a bit.

29:59.000 --> 30:00.760
- I'm going upstairs first.
- Okay.

30:16.080 --> 30:18.000
Wear your clothes properly.

30:28.760 --> 30:30.240
OVERTIME

30:30.320 --> 30:31.160
Here, He.

30:33.200 --> 30:34.200
A new dish?

30:35.080 --> 30:36.920
- What's the name of it?
- Golden Hand.

30:37.000 --> 30:39.040
- Oh, Golden Hand.
- Be careful. Don't put your fingers in.

30:39.120 --> 30:40.280
Go to hell.

30:40.360 --> 30:42.240
Boss, a new dish.

30:42.760 --> 30:45.200
Yan! Yan!

30:47.400 --> 30:48.560
- What's wrong?
- People from the Market Supervision Bureau

30:48.640 --> 30:49.840
are at the door.

30:49.920 --> 30:51.800
There are also reporters from Nanwu TV.

30:51.880 --> 30:53.080
What are they here for?

30:53.160 --> 30:54.080
A customer reported

30:54.160 --> 30:56.520
that the food made by Jun
caused food poisoning.

30:57.160 --> 30:59.000
They even called reporters to expose us.

31:00.480 --> 31:03.000
It's the program where Yifan works,
First News.

31:03.080 --> 31:04.280
How is that possible?

31:04.360 --> 31:06.480
I ate so much, and nothing happened to me.

31:07.200 --> 31:08.560
Don't worry. I'll go check it out.

31:12.720 --> 31:13.800
Hello. We're from
the Market Supervision Bureau.

31:13.880 --> 31:15.360
We've received a public complaint.

31:15.440 --> 31:17.520
Apparently, a customer here
consumed unclean ingredients.

31:17.600 --> 31:19.200
We need to take some food
and environmental samples.

31:19.280 --> 31:20.960
I'm the owner of this restaurant.

31:21.040 --> 31:22.760
If you need any cooperation, let me know.

31:22.840 --> 31:24.320
It's really you!

31:25.160 --> 31:27.600
We all ate the same dish you had at noon.

31:27.680 --> 31:29.280
Why are we fine,
but only you got food poisoning?

31:29.360 --> 31:31.600
Just because you guys are fine
doesn't mean we are!

31:31.680 --> 31:33.960
- Look at what my friend's been through!
- I saw you sneaking around at noon.

31:34.560 --> 31:35.840
And now you're framing us!

31:35.920 --> 31:36.960
Sneaking around?

31:37.040 --> 31:38.720
Your food safety is a problem!

31:38.800 --> 31:40.840
Sir, calm down.

31:40.920 --> 31:42.240
What do you want as compensation?

31:42.320 --> 31:44.280
Money, business closure,
and rectification.

31:44.360 --> 31:45.400
I can't let you

31:45.480 --> 31:48.120
heartless businesses harm more people!

31:48.200 --> 31:50.240
Otherwise, I'll make this bigger
and take it to the news!

31:51.080 --> 31:52.000
Understood.

31:52.080 --> 31:53.560
Your friend's medical fees,

31:53.640 --> 31:55.200
lost income, and mental compensation

31:55.280 --> 31:56.840
will be fully covered by our restaurant.

31:57.360 --> 31:58.480
But I have one condition.

31:58.560 --> 32:00.480
If it turns out

32:00.560 --> 32:02.400
that the food that caused
your friend's food poisoning

32:02.480 --> 32:03.920
wasn't supplied by our restaurant,

32:04.000 --> 32:05.280
I will call the reporters again.

32:05.880 --> 32:08.720
And you must publicly apologize.

32:08.800 --> 32:09.760
Deal.

32:14.320 --> 32:16.200
Jun, cooperate with them.

32:17.760 --> 32:18.960
Please follow me.

32:22.280 --> 32:24.520
Go check if there are strange ingredients.

32:24.600 --> 32:25.560
Okay.

32:31.960 --> 32:33.200
Yan…

32:34.160 --> 32:35.160
- Well…
- Fu Zhuang,

32:35.760 --> 32:37.400
can you do me a favor?

32:37.480 --> 32:40.160
- Don't tell Wen Yifan about this.
- Alright.

32:40.240 --> 32:41.360
- Thanks.
- No problem, Yan.

32:46.680 --> 32:48.240
This is Yifan's friend.

32:52.680 --> 32:53.840
Yan, we're heading out first.

32:54.480 --> 32:56.200
- We'll contact you later.
- Thanks for your hard work.

33:02.720 --> 33:04.800
Let me tell you. It's this restaurant.

33:04.880 --> 33:06.200
It's called Overtime.

33:06.280 --> 33:08.280
Their food safety is definitely a problem!

33:08.360 --> 33:09.760
As soon as my friend stepped out,

33:09.840 --> 33:11.080
he started vomiting!

33:11.160 --> 33:12.320
He just got picked up by the ambulance!

33:12.400 --> 33:14.520
How often do you do a big cleanup?

33:14.600 --> 33:16.280
We clean it thoroughly every day.

33:16.360 --> 33:18.640
- After we finish work each day,
- Yes.

33:18.720 --> 33:21.360
we clean up the kitchen completely
before we leave.

33:22.760 --> 33:25.320
Expose their place for sure!
We'll never eat at their place again!

33:25.400 --> 33:26.840
No way!

33:26.920 --> 33:30.440
We'll totally avoid these kinds
of immoral businesses!

33:30.520 --> 33:31.760
- Yes!
- Yes!

33:31.840 --> 33:33.200
Which cutting board is for meat?

33:33.280 --> 33:34.720
Which one is for vegetables?

33:34.800 --> 33:36.320
This one's for meat.

33:36.400 --> 33:37.280
This one's for vegetables.

33:37.360 --> 33:38.520
I keep them separated. I never mix them.

33:38.600 --> 33:40.120
Everything is handled separately.

33:40.200 --> 33:41.520
Hai, take a picture here.

33:41.600 --> 33:42.680
Okay.

33:42.760 --> 33:44.640
I change the ingredients every day.

33:44.720 --> 33:46.560
Absolutely no leftover ingredients.

33:47.160 --> 33:48.320
Xingde…

33:48.400 --> 33:49.840
will this kill me?

33:50.680 --> 33:51.920
What's wrong?

33:52.000 --> 33:53.640
You don't want to pay
your daughter's tuition this semester?

33:53.720 --> 33:55.120
I…

33:55.200 --> 33:56.320
Half of the compensation

33:56.400 --> 33:58.320
will go to you. Is that okay?

33:58.400 --> 34:00.200
I'll take care of it! No problem at all!

34:00.280 --> 34:01.960
Xingde, what do you think

34:02.480 --> 34:03.600
I can do?

34:05.640 --> 34:06.720
I'm also short on money.

34:08.239 --> 34:09.280
Nine pieces.

34:09.360 --> 34:10.800
Their food is really problematic.

34:10.880 --> 34:11.840
The toxicity is very strong.

34:11.920 --> 34:13.080
It made my friend feel sick
as soon as he ate it.

34:13.159 --> 34:14.639
The bigger the issue,

34:14.719 --> 34:15.880
the more compensation we'll get.

34:15.960 --> 34:17.080
- Understand?
- Understood.

34:21.679 --> 34:23.199
Before the food
investigation results come out,

34:23.280 --> 34:24.560
you must close
the business and rectify it.

34:24.639 --> 34:25.480
Close the business and rectify it?

34:35.600 --> 34:37.520
- Hello, Qiao. What happened?
- Hello, Dian.

34:37.600 --> 34:39.960
Something happened at Overtime.
Why didn't you tell me?

34:40.040 --> 34:40.880
What happened?

34:40.960 --> 34:43.199
I saw the seals on the doors.

34:43.280 --> 34:45.000
So, I called Su Haoan.

34:45.080 --> 34:48.199
He said someone
got food poisoning at Overtime.

34:48.280 --> 34:50.719
They wanted compensation,
and they even called the reporters.

34:50.800 --> 34:52.320
Fu Zhuang
and your other colleagues were there.

34:52.920 --> 34:54.199
Didn't he tell you?

34:54.280 --> 34:55.600
I've been on leave lately.

34:56.440 --> 34:57.320
He didn't tell me.

34:57.400 --> 35:00.640
I'm sure he offended someone.
That's why this happened.

35:01.600 --> 35:03.200
Alright, I get it.

35:03.280 --> 35:04.800
Let's leave it at that. Bye.

35:06.520 --> 35:08.440
Let me tell you. It's this restaurant.

35:08.520 --> 35:09.880
It's called Overtime.

35:09.960 --> 35:11.960
Their food safety is definitely a problem!

35:12.040 --> 35:13.440
As soon as my friend stepped out,

35:13.520 --> 35:14.760
he started vomiting!

35:14.840 --> 35:16.520
He just got picked up by the ambulance!

35:18.600 --> 35:20.120
Who went to Overtime?

35:20.760 --> 35:23.360
Did I delay your college admission?

35:23.440 --> 35:26.160
Or did I affect you dating
that rich boyfriend?

35:28.920 --> 35:30.160
If I can't make it through,

35:31.320 --> 35:34.000
no matter where you are, I'll find you.

35:34.080 --> 35:35.800
Let go of her!

35:36.400 --> 35:38.040
Don't you understand what I'm saying?

35:42.200 --> 35:44.040
I felt like I was dying.

35:44.760 --> 35:46.160
Each day felt like a year.

35:47.720 --> 35:49.120
See you next time.

35:51.560 --> 35:52.920
It was Che Xingde's doing.

35:58.160 --> 36:00.320
ZHAO YUANDONG

36:01.880 --> 36:02.960
Jiang,

36:03.040 --> 36:06.440
I heard from Jia
that you're dating her manager.

36:06.520 --> 36:09.600
Didn't he also open a restaurant?

36:10.440 --> 36:11.480
I heard from your uncle

36:11.560 --> 36:14.280
that the restaurant
isn't exactly respectable.

36:15.080 --> 36:16.520
Jiang, let me tell you.

36:16.600 --> 36:19.360
You can't get too close
to those shady people.

36:25.120 --> 36:27.440
- Hello, Jiang.
- Has Che Xingde been to Overtime?

36:28.080 --> 36:30.760
- I don't think so.
- I said, has Che Xingde been to Overtime?

36:31.480 --> 36:33.600
I don't know.

36:39.920 --> 36:42.800
BUILDING 7

36:47.080 --> 36:48.640
This is the last time I'm coming here.

36:50.960 --> 36:52.360
All of you…

36:53.840 --> 36:55.280
I don't want to see any of you again.

37:01.960 --> 37:03.440
Can we just live our own lives?

37:03.960 --> 37:05.160
Stop meddling with me.

37:05.240 --> 37:07.280
From now on, don't involve me!

37:08.280 --> 37:09.640
If something happens,

37:09.720 --> 37:10.920
I'm not cleaning up after you!

37:11.000 --> 37:11.920
You're so annoying!

37:12.000 --> 37:13.520
What are you complaining about, huh?
I'm the one who's annoyed!

37:19.320 --> 37:20.720
Open the door.

37:21.720 --> 37:23.240
She probably forgot her keys again.

37:25.120 --> 37:26.480
Why do you always forget them?

37:27.040 --> 37:28.200
Jiang!

37:30.560 --> 37:32.200
Why didn't you use
an umbrella in the rain?

37:38.720 --> 37:40.520
What do you want from us?

37:41.440 --> 37:42.480
I don't care

37:42.560 --> 37:44.680
why you came to Nanwu.
Just don't involve me.

37:47.360 --> 37:49.760
Live your life, and that's all.

37:49.840 --> 37:52.680
Whether you live or die,
it's none of my business.

37:55.200 --> 37:56.240
What kind of talk is that?

37:56.320 --> 37:58.040
You came in here

37:58.120 --> 37:59.320
and cursed us to death.

37:59.400 --> 38:00.560
What do you mean by that?

38:00.640 --> 38:02.040
There's nothing more to say to you.

38:03.440 --> 38:04.400
If you…

38:08.040 --> 38:09.000
or you…

38:09.920 --> 38:12.360
come bothering me
or the people around me again,

38:13.320 --> 38:14.680
I'll definitely call the police.

38:14.760 --> 38:16.440
Call the police, huh?

38:17.080 --> 38:19.240
Why do you love
calling the police so much?

38:19.960 --> 38:21.040
Let me tell you. Don't forget

38:21.120 --> 38:22.480
we once raised you!

38:22.560 --> 38:23.640
Don't stop me!

38:23.720 --> 38:25.920
How did you raise me?
Do you need me to remind you?

38:28.400 --> 38:29.480
Do you need that?

38:32.960 --> 38:35.080
Now I can finally live
without depending on anyone,

38:35.160 --> 38:36.360
working hard to live my own life.

38:36.440 --> 38:38.040
Why do you have to show up again?

38:38.120 --> 38:39.160
Jiang,

38:40.120 --> 38:41.640
your aunt…

38:42.640 --> 38:44.480
During those two years,
we really lived depending on your aunt.

38:44.560 --> 38:46.640
We can't just turn our backs on that.

38:50.880 --> 38:52.160
Che Yanqin,

38:54.560 --> 38:57.080
the surgery fees you had
were paid by my dad, right?

38:59.000 --> 39:01.360
And Wen Ming's tuition
was also paid by my dad.

39:03.000 --> 39:04.880
And the money
you needed for your business,

39:06.000 --> 39:07.080
did he ask for it back?

39:07.880 --> 39:10.320
I need to clarify this with you.

39:10.400 --> 39:13.240
All of that money
was your dad's choice to give.

39:13.320 --> 39:14.280
You don't believe it? Ask her!

39:14.360 --> 39:17.440
Ask your mom! Go ahead! Ask!

39:19.320 --> 39:20.560
And you…

39:24.320 --> 39:26.600
Why did you make me live
under someone else's roof for years?

39:31.840 --> 39:33.040
You could afford

39:34.720 --> 39:37.400
to raise me, but never
had the courage to do so.

39:39.080 --> 39:40.280
Wen Yifan,

39:41.160 --> 39:43.160
what are you saying?

39:43.960 --> 39:45.960
How did you become like this?

39:46.680 --> 39:48.520
Did you learn bad things from that guy
who runs the restaurant?

39:50.760 --> 39:51.880
Learn bad things?

39:53.360 --> 39:55.320
Now you're worried I've turned bad?

39:55.400 --> 39:56.240
Isn't it too late?

40:03.640 --> 40:05.320
I'll say it again.

40:07.880 --> 40:10.200
If you keep bothering
the people around me,

40:12.360 --> 40:13.840
I'll fight you to the end.

40:42.800 --> 40:43.720
Eight bamboos.

40:43.800 --> 40:45.720
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

40:47.360 --> 40:48.200
Four dots.

40:50.160 --> 40:51.080
I win!

41:00.720 --> 41:02.720
I'm done playing. I'm leaving now.

41:02.800 --> 41:08.160
TEA

41:25.920 --> 41:26.760
Jiang.

41:29.040 --> 41:29.960
Well…

41:30.560 --> 41:33.160
I just lost all my money playing mahjong.

41:33.240 --> 41:35.640
Can you lend me
some money for this emergency?

41:35.720 --> 41:36.840
I don't have any money.

41:37.800 --> 41:38.960
I will pay you back.

41:39.040 --> 41:40.760
- Come on. Lend me some.
- I told you I don't have money.

41:40.840 --> 41:41.960
I'll give it to you tomorrow!

41:42.040 --> 41:43.120
I really don't have any money.

41:43.200 --> 41:44.440
- I'm really in a hurry--
- I really don't have any money.

41:44.520 --> 41:45.720
Let go of me!

41:47.560 --> 41:49.080
Fine. I don't want it.

41:49.680 --> 41:51.880
When I get my salary,
I'll give you pocket money.

41:52.480 --> 41:53.520
Go home now.

42:01.560 --> 42:02.640
Wen Shuangjiang,

42:03.480 --> 42:04.400
are you okay?

42:07.000 --> 42:07.880
Who is he?

42:11.400 --> 42:12.240
I don't know him.

42:12.880 --> 42:14.080
You may go home now.

45:15.880 --> 45:16.720
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

45:16.800 --> 45:17.640
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
